description:
Bubble Shooter is a classic match three game. Your mission is to make combinations of three or more same-coloured bubbles to clear the playing field. The more bubbles you shoot at once the more points you get. You win if all bubbles are shot. 

Features:

- Beautiful and extraordinary graphics;
- Amazing game sounds;
- Specifically designed for touch-screen phones;
- High scores board (save your scores);

For those who want to play a classic intelligent game, exploding bubbles... this is the game.  Explode the bubbles and enjoy!
